      <title>全球价格暴跌，中国购买大量外国粮食</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/china-buys-hefty-amount-of-foreign-grain-as-global-prices-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去两周，中国在国际市场上抢购了 20 多批饲料谷物，作为全球最大进口国，利用价格跌至三年多来最低水平的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/china-buys-hefty-amount-of-foreign-grain-as-global-prices-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 03:55:38 GMT</pubDate>
